Package com.raweng.built

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Built
    Contains all Built API classes and functions.
    BuiltACL
    Access Control List (ACL) allows you to control who can access the content of your application.
    BuiltAnalytics
    The BuiltAnalytics class provides an interface to Built.io's analytics backend.
    BuiltAnalyticsEvent
    Helper class to set event uid and event properties required for analytics.
    BuiltApplication
    To fetch application level information of your application from Built.io Backend server.
    BuiltClass
    BuiltClass provides BuiltObject and BuiltQuery instance.
    It also provides some functionality with the Built.io Backend server.
    BuiltConfig
    Configurations of BuiltApplication class.
    BuiltError
    To retrieve information related to network call failure.
    BuiltExtension
    This class is used to make cloud related network calls.
    BuiltGroup
    A Group is special type of field in Built.io Backend.
    BuiltGroupMultiple
    A Group is special type of field in Built.io Backend.
    BuiltInstallation
    BuiltInstallation class for creating installation and subscribe/unsubscribe for push notifications against a channel.
    BuiltKeyStore
    BuiltKeyStore is maintained locally.
    BuiltLocation
    This class is used to set location while creating new object or used for making geo point related queries.
    BuiltNotification Deprecated
    BuiltObject
    BuiltObject is used to create, update and delete built object on the Built.io Backend server.
    BuiltPresence
    BuiltPresence is a feature that allows user to detect if a certain application user is currently online or offline.
    BuiltQuery
    A class that defines a query that is used to query for BuiltObject instance.
    BuiltRole
    To create, modify or delete roles on Built.io Backend server.
    BuiltSynchronousResponse Deprecated
    BuiltSyncResult
    This class is use in sync callbacks for extract data.
    BuiltUpload
    BuiltUpload class to upload media files on Built.io Backend server.
    BuiltUser
    This class allows registering user for an application and other features such as logging in and logging out.
    QueryResult
    Helper class for parsing the result of BuiltQuery
